import React from 'react';
import { Grid, GridItem } from '@patternfly/react-core';


export default class EventInfo extends React.Component {
    render() {
        return (
            <Grid >
            <GridItem span={12} className={marginboth}> Go back to Events </GridItem>
            <GridItem span={8} rowSpan={1}>
              Habitat for Humanity Fundraiser Event
            </GridItem>
            <GridItem span={4} rowSpan={3}>
              Event banner
            </GridItem>
            <GridItem span={8}> Event Description </GridItem>
            <GridItem span={8} rowSpan={4}>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit, sed do eiusmod tempor incididunt ut labore et dolore magna aliqua. Ut enim ad minim veniam, quis nostrud exercitation ullamco laboris nisi ut aliquip ex ea commodo consequat.     </GridItem>
            <GridItem span={8}> </GridItem>

            <GridItem span={8}> </GridItem>

          </Grid>

    }
}
